data.description:
Discover the allure of this Hanford home, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 baths within a comfortable 1,640 square feet of living space. The thoughtfully designed interior showcases a blend of laminate and tile flooring, offering both style and practicality. With a lot dimension of 6,623 square feet, this residence strikes a perfect balance between indoor and outdoor living.
The exterior boasts a classic stucco finish, lending a touch of sophistication to the home's facade. The durable tile roof not only enhances the overall aesthetic but also ensures longevity and resilience. This property in Hanford is more than just a house; it's a well-crafted home designed for modern living. Whether you're relaxing indoors or enjoying the outdoor spaces, this residence combines functionality with elegance, creating a welcoming haven in the heart of Hanford.
